{"tid":1116774,"cid":7,"subCid":0,"title":"葡 萄 友 劣 評 如 潮：坤 哥 條 件 唔 適 合 開 紅 館 show","createTime":"2019-04-20T08:22:31.000Z","updateTime":"2019-04-20T09:10:32.000Z","uid":35964,"like":27,"dislike":1,"uniUserReply":5,"replies":[{"pid":"5317d17e3a895298d9ba240dad49456ac2eff92d","tid":1116774,"uid":35964,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-04-20T08:22:31.000Z","msg":"<a href=\"https://www.facebook.com/karvitzmusic\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=https%3A%2F%2Fwww.facebook.com%2Fkarvitzmusic&d=v6UOKjiqNHu3M1gE0B2GLKDCEJE6krTJKQ6%2BfiBCJRk%3D&h=c4ca9c4a\" target=\"_blank\">https://www.facebook.com/karvitzmusic</a><br />\n<br />\n只是合格而矣。<br />\n <br />\n不論是唱或跳，仍然都是未夠成熟。人氣已不復當年，再繼續莽撞下去也不易遇到另一波升浪，這次《小句號》的出現，正好讓坤哥停一停諗一諗未來嘅發展。<br />\n <br />\n演唱會的銷情不理想，唯有急召外援幫手，邀得風馬牛不相及但初登紅館嘅 Mirror 作賣點也算幫到手，可惜實情是忠粉在 Mirror 演出後就匆匆散水，場面尷尬。再且，在 Mirror 一番熱舞之後，坤哥無辦法承接落去，場內氣氛一下子就變得更冷清。<br />\n <br />\n老實講，以坤哥嘅條件基本上唔適合開紅館 show，要唱要跳要表演仲要帶動埋氣氛，坤哥根本就招架不住，連佢自己在台上都話自己喜歡簡簡單單咁彈住結他唱歌。<br />\n  <br />\n如果數演唱會驚喜位，側田做嘉賓合唱〈凱旋門〉絕對是第一個，羅生一開口，首歌就立即升晒 lv。"},{"pid":"a5b84408b79745078261a361d9783230b88c2ab4","tid":1116774,"uid":49979,"like":1,"dislike":0,"score":1,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-04-20T08:26:42.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"/assets/faces/dog/smile.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/dog/haha.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"82e9650851bf6dc6f7a017a56e9ed8a424db2ccb","tid":1116774,"uid":38904,"like":7,"dislike":2,"score":5,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-04-20T08:53:56.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"https://na.cx/i/ZvTNU0V.gif\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fna.cx%2Fi%2FZvTNU0V.gif&h=8a47a3ca&s={SIZE}\" />"},{"pid":"18d87643c86e0b089f36735a3081f9c1d0504a46","tid":1116774,"uid":4574,"like":12,"dislike":0,"score":12,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-04-20T08:56:59.000Z","msg":"唔適合做藝人<br />\n<br />\n除咗扮棋"},{"pid":"b709b4bd74821d0501f5aeed030d5b87cfbd884e","tid":1116774,"uid":101253,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"20